message.body: I'm lost in NY and my credit card isn't working. Awesome!
Oh no! Where are you trying to get to?
I found my way :) running an errand for the nice extern lady
Oh cool : )
How is the major/summer plannig going?
Tough. I don't know what to do.
I'm sorry :( I'm struggling with it too. Have you talked to anyone aside from CDubb? She seems so...preoccupied
What do you want to do? Would you feel good if you could do Archaeology?
Everything I want to do is in Europe and the funding isn't enough to get me there
I know. Why can't we live in Europe already
Hahahahahahaha right!?
And New York is so competitive. I'm going to ask Peter Magee if he has any advice
How is NY?
I kind of want to go home
I got an email from Christina that stressed me out & she's been ignoring my q about how many credits I have. I'm looking forward to museum hopping on Sat!
She sent me a stressful email too. I wrote her back saying I can't afford to have any less than the credits I thought I had. No response
And yes I'm doing the externship :) the lady is super nice and it's cool, I feel silly doing this when I have so much other work to do
I don't know. I'm like not even thinking about my class content, this is all consuming
I know!!! I talked to Julie about the issues we're having the other day & she was pissed
Which is great....but I kind if just want to know what to do to resolve it. I don't really care who's pissed and who isn't, I just want to know the dilly so I can focus on my school work!
It felt good to use "the dilly" in a sentence.
It's therapeutic. I don't even know what I'm stressing about anymore haha.
Tangled confusion of stress!!
Aww my date from the other day sent me a very sweet text :) I'm sure ill find some way to absolutely ruin this!!!
Cause I'm super slick like that
Nice!
It turns out she's a premed bio major at Penn w a passion for music, theater & biking
And she dresses in drag for Shakespearean plays so...she's perfect
Wow that's great! Pretty much perfect
I'm trying to think of a fun 2nd date
And for once I'm not trying to be sleazy! New approach to dating!
Good! Sleazy doesn't work on the good ones
Don't worry: I'm aware that I'm an idiot. :) are you stoked to add to your plant family?
Sorry, I'm running late for an appointment with my accupressurist
I'm glad you got it out of your system. We all have our phases. Remember my last summer?
It's cool! Ttyl, have fun!
Good Morning! Do you have a few minutes to chat at some point today?
Yeah what's up?
